data.description: Great opportunity to own this home close to Lincoln and easy commute around with quick access to HWY 2, HWY 77 and I-80. Just minutes drive to downtown Lincoln to enjoy sports, dining and fitness facilities; and University Campus. Home has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, a large deck overseeing the garden and large backyard. Home has two car garage and lots of possibilities, located in a fast growing southwest Lincoln area. Call to schedule a showing. Thank you for your business.
